+/***************************************************************************
+ * Copyright (c) Andreas Krebbel                                            *
+ * Based on xsimd_cpu_features_ppc.hpp                                      *
+ * Copyright (c) Johan Mabille, Sylvain Corlay, Wolf Vollprecht and         *
+ * Martin Renou                                                             *
+ * Copyright (c) QuantStack                                                 *
